videos.headline: West Virginia scores pick-6 off wild deflections
videos.description: Brock Purdy's pass is batted around and picked off by Tykee Smith who returns it 19 yards for a West Virginia touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (West Virginia scores pick-6 off wild deflections) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Purdy dives for TD to give Iowa State the lead
videos.description: Brock Purdy keeps the snap and dives through the West Virginia defense into the end zone to give Iowa State a 14-7 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Purdy dives for TD to give Iowa State the lead) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Simmons stiff-arms his way to a West Virginia TD
videos.description: T.J. Simmons makes the catch and uses the stiff-arm to free himself to score a nine-yard West Virginia touchdown to tie the game at 14-14.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Simmons stiff-arms his way to a West Virginia TD) 2019/10/11 ESHEET
